  "texts": [
    "However, in the current landscape of the RS domain, there is a scarcity of high-quality image-text instruction-following data.",
    "This scarcity poses a significant obstacle when it comes to training multi-modal intelligent dialogue assistants that can achieve a high level of alignment between visual and language, unify various tasks into a framework, and integrate different multi-sensor visual modalities effectively.To address this challenge, we have constructed a dataset called MMRS-1M containing more than 1M image-text pairs, covering tasks such as classification, detection, image captioning, VQA, visual grounding, etc.",
    "MMRS-1M encompasses three visual modalities such as optical, infrared, and SAR.",
    "MMRS-1M is designed to promote the continuous development of MLLMs in the RS field.",
    "This section introduces the proposed EarthGPT framework."
  ],
